title: #92Noon! Vox In The Box/Tennabee/Boudreau/Russo/Carter
description: Paul Allen and Nordo are live from the Xcel for the Wild's practice and Vox in the Box. They are joined by the FAN's Brandon Tennabee Mileski, head coach, Bruce Boudreau, The Athletic's, Mike Russo, and FSN's Ryan Carter.
